(29071, 8, 0, "There... There's no more time for me. I'm done for. Finish me off, $n. Do it or they'll kill us both. $n... Remember Tirisfal! This world is worth saving!", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Antoine Brack", 29400),
