(49356, 0, 1, "%s whimpers.", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 29283),
(49356, 0, 2, "%s cries softly.", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 29284),
(49356, 0, 3, "%s sobs.", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 29285),
(49356, 1, 0, "C... can't we work this out somehow?", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 49380),
(49356, 2, 0, "Alright, j... just let me... let me st... stand up.", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 49381),
(49356, 3, 0, "$n?", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 49382),
(49356, 4, 0, "$n, I'd recognize that face anywhere... What... What have they done to you, $n?", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 49383),
(49356, 5, 0, "You don't remember me, $n? I lost count of the number of jobs you and I ran back in the day on Kezan. Then I picked up a real bad Kaja'Cola habit and you saved me! It was you who took me to Kalimdor to join the Steamwheedle Cartel. You were the only good goblin I knew. That's how I ended up in the Argent Dawn, because I knew it was what you woulda done. How could this have happened to you?", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 49384),
(49356, 6, 0, "Remember the goblin that you once were, $g brother:sister;! You were my best friend! Fight this!", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 49385),
(49356, 7, 0, "Listen to me, $n. You must fight against the Lich King's control. He is a monster that wants to see this world - our world - in ruin. Don't let him use you to accomplish his goals. You were once a hero and you can be again. Fight, damn you! Fight his control!", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 49386),
(49356, 8, 0, "There... There's no more time for me. I'm done for. Finish me off, $n. Do it or they'll kill us both. $n... Remember Kezan, our beloved home. This world is worth saving.", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 49387),
(49356, 9, 0, "Do it, $n! Put me out of my misery!", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 49388),
(49356, 10, 0, "%s dies from his injuries.", 12, 0, 100, 0, 0, 0, "Gally Lumpstain", 49389);
